quran[5{c,v,t}:
6,69,"unn ke hisaab mein se kisi cheez ki zimma daari parhaiz gaar logon par nahi hai, Albata nasiyaat karna unn ka farz hai shayad ke woh ghalat rawi se bach jayen"
6,70,"chhorro unn logon ko jinhon ne apne deen ko khail aur tamasha bana rakha hai aur jinhein duniya ki zindagi fraib mein mubtala kiye hue hai haan magar yeh quran suna kar nasiyaat aur tanbeeh karte raho ke kahin koi shakhs apne kiye krtoton ke wabaal mein girftar nah ho jaye, aur girftar bhi iss haal mein ho ke Allah se bachanay wala koi haami o madad gaar aur koi safarishi is ke liye nah ho, aur gir woh har mumkin cheez Fidya mein day kar chhotna chahay to woh bhi is se qubool nah ki jaye, kyunkay aisay log to khud apni kamaai ke nateeja mein pakdae jayen ge, un ko to apne inkaar haq ke muawza mein kholta howa pani peenay ko aur dard naak azaab bhgtne ko miley ga"
6,71,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se po chhoo kya hum Allah ko chore kar unn ko pukaarain jo nah hamein naffa day satke hain nah nuqsaan? aur jabkay Allah hamein seedha rasta dikha chuka hai to kya ab hum ultay paon phir jayen? kya hum apna haal uss shakhs ka sa kar len jisay shaitano ne sehraa mein bhatka diya ho aur woh heran o srgrdan phir raha hodar-aa-nhala-n keh is ke saathi usay pukaar rahay hon ke idher aa yeh seedhi raah mojood hai? kaho, haqeeqat mein sahih rahnumai to sirf Allah hi ki rahnumai hai aur is ki taraf se hamein yeh hukum mila hai ke maalik kaayenaat ke agay sir itaat khham kar do"
6,72,"namaz qaim karo aur is ki nafarmani se bachcho, isi ki taraf tum samete jao ge"
6,73,"wohi hai jis ne aasman o zameen ko Bar haq peda kya hai aur jis daal noon woh kahe ga ke hashar ho jaye isi din woh ho jaye ga is ka irshad ain haq hai aur jis roz sor phonka jaayegaa is roz basshahi usi ki hogi, woh ghaib aur shahadat har cheez ka aalam hai aur Dana aur bakhabar hai"
